summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the City Comptroller to draw and the City Treasurer to pay a warrant in the sum of Fifty Dollars ($50.00), in favor of Everett Reed, owner of Lots Thirty-eight (38) and Thirty-nine (39), Block Fifteen (15), Green Lake Circle Railroad Addition to The City of Seattle, for adjusting the existing improvements and moving the house on said Lots to conform with the official survey of the City of Seattle.
